></p><p>该曲目是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-jamie-xx-and-honey-dijon-new-single-baddy-on-the-floor-3618452">Honey Dijon 合作的前几首单曲“Baddy On The Floor”</a> 、“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jamie-xx-announces-first-new-album-in-nine-years-in-waves-along-with-uk-headline-show-3762465">Treat Each Other Right</a> ”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-jamie-xxs-collaborative-single-with-robyn-life-3766418">Robyn 合作的“Life”之后</a>的单曲。</p><p>其他消息方面，Jamie xx 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jamie-xx-announces-the-floor-residencies-in-new-york-and-la-buy-tickets-3775698">“The Floor”五晚驻场演出将于今晚在洛杉矶开始</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，这位音乐家最近透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-xx-are-having-a-good-time-working-on-new-album-says-jamie-xx-3775555">The xx 目前正在录音室“玩得很开心”，准备他们的下一张专辑</a>。 “我认为当我们进一步投入时会很困难，但最终会让记录变得更好，”他解释道。</p><p>此次更新是在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy-madley-croft">Romy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oliver-sim">Oliver Sim</a>完成的 The xx <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/romy-and-oliver-sim-reunite-with-jamie-xx-at-glastonbury-2024-set-3769976">在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 Jamie 演出期间重聚于舞台</a>之后发布的。这是他们自2018年以来首次同台演出。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jamie-xx-teams-up-with-avalanches-for-pulsing-new-single-all-you-children-3779362">Jamie xx 与 Avalanches 合作推出的新单曲“All You Children”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
